<p itemprop="description">A lead application operations engineer provides strategic leadership for application operations across multiple teams and services. They establish organisational standards, drive innovation in operational practices, and ensure alignment with business objectives.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide strategic leadership for application operations across the organisation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish organisational standards and frameworks for application operations</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive innovation and continuous improvement in operational practices</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead cross-functional initiatives to improve service reliability</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Represent application operations in senior leadership forums</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop and execute strategic plans for operational capabilities</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Ensure alignment between operational activities and business objectives</li>
    </ul>
</section>

